<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title><%= title %></title>
	<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen bg-stone-50 text-stone-800">
	<div class="relative flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center overflow-hidden px-6 py-10">
		<div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
			<div class="absolute -left-20 top-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-rose-100/60 blur-3xl"></div>
			<div class="absolute right-0 top-1/4 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-amber-100/50 blur-3xl"></div>
			<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/3 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-stone-200/50 blur-3xl"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="relative w-full max-w-2xl">
			<div
				class="overflow-hidden rounded-[32px] border border-stone-200/80 bg-white/90 shadow-2xl shadow-stone-200/50 backdrop-blur">
				<div
					class="border-b border-stone-100 bg-gradient-to-r from-rose-50 via-white to-amber-50 px-6 py-6 sm:px-8 sm:py-7">
					<div
						class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-rose-200 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-rose-700 shadow-sm">
						Server Error
					</div>

					<h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-900 sm:text-4xl">
						500 - Internal Server Error
					</h1>

					<p class="mt-3 max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600 sm:text-base">
						Terjadi kesalahan di server saat memproses halaman ini. Bukan salah kamu — sistemnya sedang bermasalah atau
						ada proses yang gagal dijalankan.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="px-6 py-8 sm:px-8 sm:py-8">
					<div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
						<div class="rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 p-4">
							<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-stone-500">Status</p>
							<p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">500</p>
						</div>

						<div class="rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 p-4">
							<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-stone-500">Condition</p>
							<p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">Server Error</p>
						</div>

						<div class="rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 p-4">
							<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-stone-500">Suggestion</p>
							<p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-stone-900">Try Again</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
						<a href="/dashboard"
							class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-stone-900 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-stone-300/40 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-rose-700">
							Go to Dashboard
						</a>

						<a href="javascript:location.reload()"
							class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-stone-300">
							Reload Page
						</a>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-stone-50 p-4">
						<p class="text-sm leading-7 text-stone-600">
							Coba refresh halaman ini beberapa saat lagi. Kalau error tetap muncul, kemungkinan ada masalah di route,
							database, atau proses server yang perlu dicek.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>

</html>